The Recipient shall not later than thirty (30) days after the Effective Date establish the Project Steering Committee with amandate, resources, terms of reference and functions, satisfactory to the Association, and thereafter, maintain said ProjectSteering Committee throughout the Project implementation.

The Recipient, by no later than one hundred eighty (180) days after the Effective Date, appoint external monitoring and evaluationexperts ("Independent Verification Agent"), to act as third-party verifiers of proper implementation of the Financing FacilityunderPart B of the Project.
